c: 3
v: 20
t: "Ubwo nibakugisha impaka (yewe Muhamadi) uzababwire uti \"Nicishije bugufi kuri Allah (ndi Umuyisilamu), (njye)n’abankurikiye\". Unabwire abahawe ibitabo n’abatazi gusoma no kwandika uti \"Ese namwe mwicishije bugufi kuri Allah?\" Nibaramuka babaye Abayisilamu, bazaba bayobotse; ariko nibahakana, rwose icyo ushinzwe ni ugusohoza ubutumwa, kandi Allah ni Ubona abagaragu be bihebuje"